        <h2 class="mb-2">OEM Compatibility Index</h2>
        <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-light mb-6">Reference index of OEM platform families commonly discussed when sourcing aftermarket replacement chuck assemblies and capping headsets. Final interchangeability should be confirmed against the exact machine model, spindle geometry, and closure format.</p>

